Device-USB-Relay version 0.01
=============================

Device::USB::Relay allows your PC to control an 8-port Relay board from
http://www.sigma-shop.com/

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules.  However, this only works on perl
on Linux at this moment.


